The english subs are embedded in the movie. You want swedish subs, go ahead and activate them but the english subs are still there. 

The sound is out of sync the last 40minutes. Makes it unwathcable imo, too bad cause the quality is otherwise fine.

As for Paramount chasing people over this torrent its not true. They actually want people to download this one, at least in Sweden they do. This movie went up at cinemas in USA in the early december and they decided to release it in Sweden in late february. 
Considering the high usage of internet in the latter country the only credible conclusion for that odd strategy I can come up with must be that they want swedes to download it. Clearly they cant expect people to see it at the theatres when its already old.
